@startuml
title 充电计费单元 - 主要进程框架

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #4A4A4A
  FontColor #222222
}
left to right direction

rectangle "MQTT Broker\n(mosquitto)\n<<核心路由总线>>" as MQ #FFF2CC

component "tcu_logic\n(core/tcu_logic)" as LOGIC
component "tcu_pile_controller\n(core/pile_controller)" as PILE
component "tcu_meter\n(core/meter)" as METER
component "tcu_comm\n(core/comm/<Platform>)" as COMM
component "logger\n(core/logger)" as LOGGER
component "daemon\n(core/daemon)" as DAEMON

cloud "充电桩主控\n(CAN2CCU)" as CCU
cloud "网络桩设备\n(UDP/TCP)" as NET_PILE
cloud "串口桩设备\n(RS485/Modbus)" as SERIAL_PILE
cloud "桩侧MQTT代理\n(可选)" as PILE_MQTT
cloud "DLT645 电表\n(RS485)" as METER_HW
cloud "平台主站\n(TCP/私有协议)" as PLAT
actor "HMI" as HMI

HMI --> MQ : tcu/logic/{gun}/cmd
MQ --> LOGIC : logic/+/cmd\nplat/+/cmd\npile/+/event\npile/+/data\nmeter/+/data
LOGIC --> MQ : tcu/pile/{gun}/cmd\n tcu/logic/{gun}/event\n tcu/logic/{gun}/feeData

MQ --> PILE : tcu/pile/{gun}/cmd
PILE --> MQ : tcu/pile/{gun}/event\n tcu/pile/{gun}/data
PILE --> CCU : CAN 接入
CCU --> PILE : 状态/响应/遥测
PILE --> NET_PILE : UDP/TCP 接入
NET_PILE --> PILE : 状态/响应/遥测
PILE --> SERIAL_PILE : RS485 接入
SERIAL_PILE --> PILE : 状态/响应/遥测
PILE <--> PILE_MQTT : MQTT 接入(可选)

METER --> METER_HW : 645轮询
METER_HW --> METER : 电量/电压/电流
METER --> MQ : tcu/meter/{gun}/data\n tcu/meter/{gun}/event

COMM --> PLAT : 平台上行帧
PLAT --> COMM : 平台下行帧
COMM --> MQ : tcu/plat/{gun}/cmd\n tcu/plat/{gun}/event
MQ --> COMM : logic/+/event\n logic/+/feeData\n pile/+/data\n pile/+/event\n meter/+/data

LOGIC --> LOGGER : logTradeRecord(...)
COMM --> LOGGER : confirmTradeRecord(...)
DAEMON --> LOGIC : 进程守护
DAEMON --> PILE : 进程守护
DAEMON --> METER : 进程守护
DAEMON --> COMM : 进程守护

note bottom of COMM
每个平台独立目录实现：
core/comm/ChangzhouLiyangSmartcityPlat
core/comm/Zhongshihua2.0
end note

note right of PILE
多方式接入能力：
- CAN / CAN2CCU
- UDP / TCP
- RS485 / Modbus
- MQTT(可选透传)
通过统一 MQTT 主题对外输出
end note

note top of MQ
核心路由职责：
- 进程解耦
- Topic 级路由与广播
- QoS 保障命令可靠性
end note

@enduml
